text: Toykino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Toykinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 295 as of 2010.ВПН-2010. Численность и размещение населения Пермского края There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km south- west from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Toykino
